snippet: Over the last 10 days, Bosnia has experienced its largest social unrest in nearly 20 years. Thousands of demonstrators have taken to the streets to assail the country's political elite....

headline.print_headline: In Bosnia, Are Outsiders the Answer, or the Problem?
headline.main: In Bosnia, Are Outsiders the Answer, or the Problem?

lead_paragraph: Over the last 10 days, Bosnia has experienced its largest social unrest in nearly 20 years. Thousands of demonstrators have taken to the streets to assail the country's political elite.
